{
  "stem": "9489.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we build up these things, they told us they need chauffeurs for the frontier.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're going to open up jungles in Zlatoust.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're going to open up jungles for they need the wood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I volunteer to be a chauffeur.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That took a year.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Before--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "School.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no-- the school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Six months theory and six months practice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got the-- I got with me the license, 924.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Want me to show you the license?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the-- At the end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, I got the license.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then, in Russia, to have a license-- chauffeur license-- was like, here in Canada, Rothschild.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who was the richest man in America?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rockefeller.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK, near of Rothschild.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You got a passport to be a multibillionaire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So famous was a chauffeur.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why you can't get it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like I told you, you have to go in a school there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Engineering, technique, then-- then you go practice a half year.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then you go to a test.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When you work off on that test-- we were about 48 or 50 students.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Just eight or 12 got the license from us, from the whole school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There's 12 people sitting there, and everybody's shooting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You're sitting in a chair like I sit here, with a white shirt, and questions right and left.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then you get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, after finish, then they tell you who passed and who didn't pass.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The nicest thing I liked, that from the 12 people was the chief in KGB.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I got the signature there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Can't-- can't deny it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in the-- and the license.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when the kids, what we got the license, they took us in for a meeting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we got juice there, you know, and beautiful pastry.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
